 READING

 April 17 at G.D. Birla Sabhagar; 11 am: Professor P. Lal reads Sanjaya?s account of the Krauncha battle formation which Yudhisthira, on Krishna?s advice, devises to counter Bhisma?s offensive, and the stalemate that results when disciple Arjuna attacks guru Bhisma, in the 274th weekly session of his complete English transcreation of Vyasa?s Mahabharata. 

